snippet.title: ANCESTORS: The Humankind Odyssey E3 TEASER 2015
snippet.description:
Ancestors: The Humankind Odyssey  is a third person action-adventure survival game. 
The player will relive the early story of mankind with a documentary twist. Humanity is one idea away from evolution or extinction...
 
Stay tuned much more to come in 2017!
